SEMDL Help Topic: reference annotate

Usage:
- `ssd annotate <selector> <kind> <text> --target sidecar <file>`
- `ssd annotate <selector> <kind> <text> --target sidecar --dry-run <file>`

Purpose:
- Append or preview rationale, caveat, todo, status, or explanation metadata.

Related help:
- `ssd help grammar`
- `ssd help samples`

Sample:
- `ssd annotate id:H1 todo 追加入力で主体を確認する --target sidecar docs/examples/minimal.ssd`
